<add>redt</add> als gelimppflıch darauf <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / daʒ vvir gemaint <expan>hett<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_486_r1l23">Jr des an die <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vnd frawen nicht braht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
