</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Lucz, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des
                                <expan>Hag<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Kürsn<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                        ir das an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frawen
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Wirtemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> braht habt. Nu
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ew vormals, als ir da von mit uns
                            <add>redt</add>, als gelimppflich darauf
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz wir gemaint
                            <expan>hett<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ir des an die
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> und frawen nicht braht
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dörfft. Dann <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> unser <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ist
                        czü <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czeit nicht anheim und, wenn er herheim
                        kümt, ist <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz uns
                            <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> daran mant, so <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir sein red hören und ew <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lasse<ex>n.</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
